## Configuration examples

### Minimal production values

```yaml
image:
  tag: "0.2.0"

secrets:
  autoGenerate: false

existingSecret: "agentregistry-secrets"

database:
  bundled:
    persistence:
      storageClass: "standard"
      size: 20Gi
      keepOnUninstall: true

resources:
  requests:
    cpu: 250m
    memory: 256Mi
  limits:
    cpu: 500m
    memory: 512Mi
```

### External database

```yaml
database:
  bundled:
    enabled: false
  external:
    host: "pg.example.com"
    database: "agent-registry"
    username: "agentregistry"
    existingSecret: "pg-secret"
    sslMode: "require"
```

### Namespace-scoped RBAC

```yaml
rbac:
  clusterScoped: false
```

